title: Woman In Motorized Wheelchair Medium Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Woman In Electric Wheelchair Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: A woman using a motorized wheelchair, representing mobility, independence, and accessibility. The medium-dark skin tone modifier indicates a specific skin color.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts a woman with a medium-dark skin tone confidently seated in a motorized wheelchair, rendered with Apple's signature soft rounded edges and realistic lighting. The wheelchair itself has a sleek, modern design with subtle glossy 3D shading, conveying a sense of independence and capability. This emoji is a powerful representation of accessibility, empowerment, and inclusivity in digital conversations.
